01:16:37.123 --> 01:16:41.597
U redu. Da... Brže. I ovaj put...

01:16:42.712 --> 01:16:44.754
Hajde!

01:16:48.259 --> 01:16:52.477
Slatko. O.K. Pazite na ovaj stup.

01:16:54.265 --> 01:16:56.802
Tri, dva, jedan.

